title: My GPF 5.1.1
text:
My GPF 5.1.1
กองทุนบำเหน็จบำนาญข้าราชการ– Freeware – Android
The GPF Mobile Platform is a comprehensive service designed for members of the Government Pension Fund (GPF). With just a touch, you can access your retirement plan and enjoy the convenience of member services. Additionally, the platform offers a range of exclusive privileges for GPF members.
Key features of the GPF Mobile Platform include:
- Viewing account savings transactions
- Selecting or changing investment plans
- Digital membership card to enjoy discounts and benefits from partnering merchants
- Access to financial information and resources to promote savings and financial literacy
- Income planning and evaluation tools for retirement
- Financial consultation appointment scheduling
- Chatbot support for problem-solving
If you have any inquiries or need assistance with the platform, we recommend contacting the GPF Contact Center at 1179 or connecting through Line: @GPFcommunity.
